**Step 1**: Define a class `CircularQueue` with `arr[MAX]`, `front`, `rear`. Initialize `front = -1, rear = -1`.

**Step 2**: Implement `isFull()` as `((rear + 1) % MAX == front)`. Implement `isEmpty()` as `front == -1`.

**Step 3**: Implement `enqueue(int x)`:
